<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.6">
<l>kalai yuṭutta vakalal kulvaṉpēy makaḷtāyeṉa</l>
<l>mulai koṭuttā ḷuyiruṇ ṭavaṉvā ḻiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>kulai yeṭutta katalip poḻilū ṭumvantuntimuṉ</l>
<l>alai yeṭukkum puṉaṟkā viricūḻ teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place where lives the one who consumed the life</l>
<l rend="indent">of the strong demon woman,</l>
<l>Whose wide hips were clothed in a girdle, the one who offered her breast</l>
<l rend="indent">like a mother,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South encircled by the Kāviri with waters where waves rise,</l>
<l>Coming into the gardens, casting forward banana trees</l>
<l rend="indent">which bear clusters [of fruit].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
